title: Alicia Vikander
summary: Alicia Amanda Vikander (/vɪˈkændər/,[1] Swedish: [aˈlǐːsɪa vɪˈkǎnːdɛr] (listen); born 3 October 1988) is a Swedish actress. She has won various awards, including an Academy Award and a Screen Actors Guild Award, nominations for two Golden Globe Awards and three British Academy Film Awards.
